<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>VAN CUNG PENNAK KAWL HMASA</title>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ( Van cung pennak, le, a, dinnak kha
 Zeidang vialte, nak in,
 Kawl hmasa u, law, nan hna a ngam lai
 Hallelui, Hallelui-jah.) 2

[V2]
 ( Mi nung hi rawl, lawng, in, a nung lo
 Pathian bia in, a nung,
 Cu bia tak nih, cun, luatnak an pek lai
 Hallelui, Hallelui-jah.) 2

[V3]
 ( King u law inn, ka, awn, nan si lai
 Kawl u law nan, hmuh lai,
 Hal u law nan, hmuh, lai tiah a ti
 Hallelui, Hallelui-jah.) 2

[V4]
 ( Bawipa kha na, lung, chung, dihlak in
 I bochan zung-zal law,
 A mah nih na, lam, kha a tluanter lai
 Hallelui, Hallelui-jah.) 2

[C1]
   ( Halleluijah, Halleluijah, Halleluijah
   Hallelui, Halleluijah ) 2</lyrics>
</song>